<small>(close to Memphis)</small></th>
<th width="25%" style="background-color: #ccffcc">26% of voters<br />
<small>(close to Nashville)</small></th>
<th width="25%" style="background-color: #ddddff">15% of voters<br />
<small>(close to Chattanooga)</small></th>
<th width="25%" style="background-color: #ffeedd">17% of voters<br />
<small>(close to Knoxville)</small></th>
</tr>
