<li><a href="http://pj.freefaculty.org/Ukraine/PJ3_VotingSystemsEssay.pdf" class="external text" title="http://pj.freefaculty.org/Ukraine/PJ3_VotingSystemsEssay.pdf" rel="nofollow">Voting Systems</a> by Paul E. Johnson</li>
<li><a href="http://www.eskimo.com/~robla/politics/condorcet.html" class="external text" title="http://www.eskimo.com/~robla/politics/condorcet.html" rel="nofollow">Condorcet's Method</a> By Rob Lanphier</li>
<li><a href="http://accuratedemocracy.com/" class="external text" title="http://accuratedemocracy.com/" rel="nofollow">Accurate Democracy</a> by Rob Loring</li>
<li><a href="http://www1.fee.uva.nl/creed/pdffiles/MoulinCh4Elferink.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www1.fee.uva.nl/creed/pdffiles/MoulinCh4Elferink.pdf" rel="nofollow">Voting and Social Choice</a> by HervÃ© Moulin. Demonstration and commentary on Condorcet method.</li>
<li><a href="http://www.cs.cornell.edu/andru/civs.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cs.cornell.edu/andru/civs.html" rel="nofollow">CIVS, a free web poll service using the Condorcet method</a> by Andrew Myers</li>
<li><a href="http://stv.sourceforge.net/" class="external text" title="http://stv.sourceforge.net/" rel="nofollow">Software for computing Condorcet methods and STV</a> by Jeffrey O'Neill</li>
<li><a href="http://www2.uah.es/docecon/documentos/DT1.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www2.uah.es/docecon/documentos/DT1.pdf" rel="nofollow">A Strong No Show paradox is a common flaw in Condorcet voting correspondences</a> by Joaquin Perez.</li>
<li><a href="http://radicalcentrism.org/majority_voting.html" class="external text" title="http://radicalcentrism.org/majority_voting.html" rel="nofollow">Maximum Majority Voting</a> by Ernest Prabhakar</li>
<li><a href="http://www.citizensassembly.bc.ca/resources/submissions/csharman-10_0409201706-143.pdf" class="external text" title="http://www.citizensassembly.bc.ca/resources/submissions/csharman-10_0409201706-143.pdf" rel="nofollow">A New Monotonic and Clone-Independent Single-Winner Election Method</a> (<a href="http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/demexp-dev/2003-09/pdflQW7IlpAfC.pdf" class="external text" title="http://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/demexp-dev/2003-09/pdflQW7IlpAfC.pdf" rel="nofollow">1</a>, <a href="http://www.mcdougall.org.uk/VM/ISSUE17/I17P3.PDF" class="external text" title="http://www.mcdougall.org.uk/VM/ISSUE17/I17P3.PDF" rel="nofollow">2</a>) by Markus Schulze</li>
</ul>


